                    <span id="c-924911020" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-924911020" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="924911020">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/usewelltheday/">若迦</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-05-23</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">目前读了前三本，这本是相对最好的。虽然行文的腔调还是不大舒服。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="799335952">
